  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Silberhorn is on half board. </p>
<p>Each day you can enjoy an extensive breakfast buffet with hot and cold options. Dinner includes a four course evening meal with a choice of main course with vegetarian options available. There is a weekly buffet evening with various dishes available. </p>
<p>Christmas dinner, and a New Years gala buffet dinner is included. </p>
<p>The Hotel also has an a la carte restaurant: the Silberhornstube (pay locally)</p>]]></cateringDescription>
