  <description><![CDATA[<p>Situated in the centre of Wengen, just opposite the mountain railway station and within close proximity to the Männlichen cable car, the Silberhorn is an ideal base to access the Jungfrau Ski Area. Offering a good standard of 'ski in' accommodation, cuisine and spa facilities, it has been a favourite with Inghams guests in recent years.</p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>Located in the centre of the village, the Silberhorn is the perfect starting point for skiers and boarders looking for accommodation with access to the renowned <a data-udi="umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656}" title="Jungfrau Ski Region">Jungfrau Ski Region</a>. The nursery slopes and the Männlichen cable car is less than 100 metres away, taking you up to the summit station - admire the incredible views of the <span>Eiger, Mönch and Jungfrau and then enjoy a day of exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a>, Kleine Scheidegg. The mountain railway is just opposite the hotel, from here you can head up to the Jungfraujoch Top of Europe or to Lauterbrunnen for picturesque views and access to <a data-udi="umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc}" title="Murren">Mürren</a>.</span></p>
<h2>Spa and relaxation</h2>
<p><span>After a day of exploring the Jungfrau Region, rejuvenate in the wellness area. Unwind and relax in the sauna and steam room or soothe your muscles in the Jacuzzi after a day of outdoor adventures. If you want a moment of peace, sit back and relax with panoramic views of the Lauterbrunnen valley. There is also a fitness room with a range of equipment so you can stay active, even when you are not skiing, boarding or walking. For the ultimate treat, book a massage with one of the masseuses. </span></p>
<h2><span>Modern comforts </span></h2>
<p>The<span> Hotel Silberhorn offers comfortable accommodation blending traditional Swiss architecture and modern amenities. Its wooden facades, incredible views and cosy interiors create an inviting atmosphere that captures the essence of Alpine charm. </span>You can choose from a variety of rooms, including spacious twin rooms with views of the Jungfrau or family rooms with additional beds. Each room has cosy alpine décor, and all rooms are equipped with modern amenities such as TVs with English speaking channels, free Wi-Fi, and tea and coffee making facilities.</p>]]></description>
