  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior North Facing Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people and are around 25m². These rooms have twin beds or a king size bed, and an additional single sofa bed, with village views and a bath.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Jungfrau Twin Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people and are around 25m². These rooms have twin beds or a king size bed, and an additional single sofa bed, with a balcony with views of the Jungfrau.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 27m². These rooms have twin beds, and an additional double sofa bed, and a balcony with views of the Jungfrau.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Jungfrau View Rooms are available for </strong>single occupancy and are around 15m². These rooms have a balcony with views of the Jungfrau.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath with showerhead attachment</li>
<li>WC</li>
